Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.46,0:01:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明年的秋天 還能看得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太陽早去睡覺 星星月亮就會通宵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:02:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在晚上之前結束所有祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}耶魯節之夜就要來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.51,0:02:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你好 夜之愛子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能做好耶魯節的準備嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}耶魯節？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在就去做耶魯節的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這個瞌睡蟲 耶魯節很快就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.03,0:02:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要燃燒耶魯的柴薪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在黑色女神和冥府之鹿走上原野之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你們 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.67,0:02:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安 艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她們是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.59,0:02:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}耶魯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.61,0:02:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她們總會在冬至到來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我叫她們耶魯的雙子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過不知道她們到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天會很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:02:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}累了要跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.76,0:03:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我一定會說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不配當使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:16.69,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世有危險時 我什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他一直都這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:20.35,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣沒意義吧 我已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你比我更了解智世吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世會對我隱瞞 你可能也不好告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.26,0:03:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是你可以早點跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如此一來 我就想辦法處理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.00,0:03:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是尷尬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她的身體還有點冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為剛從外面回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}開始準備耶魯節吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就是漂亮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是這麼覺得的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在檞寄生枝下接吻是種傳統習俗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}試試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他好像很想試
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你可以彎下腰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}換我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在背後 還是腰部 有一種癢癢的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼問這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路茲也來一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來吃晚餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老爺 您的東西我收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思 每次都拖到最後一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.74,0:07:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會 這點事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒問題 已經留了紙條
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.86,0:07:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人好多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 我先進到裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.07,0:08:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思啊 把你叫到倫敦來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.22,0:08:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼 是…關於聖誕禮物的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}送給連富烈德的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你真的不知道送什麼好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前送什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}反而是他送我禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我想今年送他點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直在吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吃得好猛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你…你不送些什麼給那個骷髏頭嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完全沒想過…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼 今天我們就一起去挑禮物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一臉要我陪著的意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有找到好東西嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.81,0:09:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有 畢竟要考慮到他的喜好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.14,0:09:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其實我根本不知道他的喜好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我從沒送禮物給什麼人過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是…沒什麼認識的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身邊沒有這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.13,0:09:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那現在 我和智世就是同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然魔法和魔術不同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但都是跟著師父學習生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:09:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這不是恩滋華斯老爺家的小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}黑澤爾先生 您好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}智世 你在和誰說話？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呀 和您一起的那位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}魔術師和魔法使不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他們看不到施展了隱身魔法的我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}初次見面 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聖誕禮物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}選個能想像出對方使用的樣子的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.74,0:11:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仔細回想一下對方 想想最適合的東西是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們再去逛一圈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}平常使用的東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我好像想到了一個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好狡猾 快告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不能學我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這不是愛麗絲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們走 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了 跟以前一樣和我玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我已經不碰毒品了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.62,0:11:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}從…從哪裡冒出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:11:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 他們是我以前的狐群狗黨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}毒品很好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好吃 不合我的口味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也不是喜歡才去吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在都覺得是做了場夢而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這種事沒什麼意思 不說了不說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我被混蛋父母逼著吸食毒品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原本只有當毒販這一條路可走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是師父收留了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 你有沒有看到一個金髮的小鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我得好好教訓她一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你看什麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想一直待在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.59,0:13:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還沒和你自我介紹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我叫米海爾‧連富烈德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}隨便你怎麼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先洗個澡再說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那時候我還完全不相信師父
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前一直生活在垃圾場般的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}信任他人 對我來說是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}書名看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是說了不要翻開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.44,0:15:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.31,0:15:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 我也有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是我沒有下明確的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你受傷了 臉上…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:15:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是幸好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你好不容易恢復了健康
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可不能再受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.22,0:16:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我習慣幫人治傷了 能做好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然都是自學的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下次我會好好做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要作為守護者 保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下次就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回想起來真是不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不知道該說什麼才好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不需要你去考慮什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的幸福還是不幸 是你自己決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你聽我說了這些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說有沒有一隻使魔鳥 飛到你那裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很小隻的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}算了 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會再寫信的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你陪我到這麼晚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不會 也謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:17:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望我們都順利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你交到朋友真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大哥哥覺得她合格嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}倒不是個壞傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 伊森
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}史黛拉 伊森
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們也回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}歡迎回來 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回來得真晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我回來了 艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有什麼想要的東西值得跑去倫敦一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還和連富烈德的弟子見了面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.97,0:18:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你知道你都碰過多少危險了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}居然還什麼都不說就出門
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我怕你不同意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.72,0:18:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我肯定會的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:18:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有我跟著的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用這麼生氣 艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}生氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我在生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可能是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.49,0:19:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 我是為了去買這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然早了一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聖誕快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.67,0:19:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艾利亞斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊 沒想到你會送我禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前沒想過要給你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 艾利亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}呃…你一直都戴著同樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.27,0:19:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想說這能讓你安心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是你不喜歡的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:19:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也給你一份
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.61,0:20:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然只幫安潔莉卡她們做過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但這次我想給你也做一個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是你親手做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.49,0:20:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.87,0:20:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}安潔莉卡以前和我說過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想要熊布偶作為禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今年做的這個 應該是做得最好的一個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難道從那開始就一直在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 其他東西我都不太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有點小機關哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有那些 都是大家給你的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}安潔莉卡 賽門 還有林德爾的都送來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}禮物原本都是要當天拆開的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以這些明天再拆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:20:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了 先吃晚餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說教就等到晚餐後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他還記著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.15,0:21:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是你告訴我 我會跟著去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還能買不少東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.86,0:21:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.08,0:21:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為有些話只能和同為女孩子的人說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聖誕節似乎本來就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}難以置信 我竟然會期待明天的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.91,0:22:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有個可憐的孩子啊
Comment: 0,0:22:24.93,0:22:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,ED-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.08,0:22:33.09,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}月は見ていた　欠けてる僕ら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.21,0:22:37.75,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}互いを呼び合いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.06,0:22:47.26,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}遠回りで　遠い道を歩いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.44,0:22:57.55,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}引きよせ合う　赤と黒が
